Offering SIM management solutions to various industries and specialising in M2M, telemetry and IoT applications, Flickswitch has almost 10 years of experience on the continent. &#x201c;We are very proud to represent Flickswitch for their PR and communication needs, and we look forward to working with their team of exceptional professionals,&#x201d; says Nicole Capper, owner and director of MANGO-OMC. Hein Koen, director at Flickswitch, says, &#x201c;PR remains an important part of the marketing communications mix - telling the good stories of our company as well as those of our customers.&#x201d;